THE PLANCK GRAIN · node GRN · GRN · THE PLANCK GRAIN · techne · the pixel of spacetime · UD0 / techne

universe of origin : the art — a generative rendering of a scale
seal               : Is space continuous, or is it grainy — made of smallest indivisible units, like the pixels of a screen? Some approaches to quantum gravity (loop quantum gravity among them) suggest that at the Planck scale, area and volume come in discrete chunks. This sphere draws that conjecture as art: a tessellated grain, one cell lit, the would-be pixel of reality.
